{"tid":245642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人嘅老豆老母會講仔女壞話?","createTime":"2017-05-16T11:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T13:35:17.000Z","uid":37005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c58a831fe7f3987f87b7d0e8b8631ba10561331","tid":245642,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"我老豆老母會喺呀哥面前講家姐 我面前講返呀哥 總之邊個唔在場就講邊個<br />\n真係好撚賤 成日覺得點解我嘅老豆老母會咁異於常人<br />\n人地嗰啲會好錫仔女 仔女有困難會支持體諒關心<br />\n但我嗰兩個唔會 仲要講埋啲嘢難聽到仆街<br />\n竟然有老母會話自己個親生仔似智障 又會話自己個親生女做雞都冇人屌<br />\n睇錢大過天 邊個俾錢佢洗就邊個乖 你老味有時真係好撚憎佢地 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bd89fc0aecca9438215dd1de73071443cd4502","tid":245642,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我面前態度正正常常 有時行開下eg沖涼之後再返來 會偷聽到老豆老母講我壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要講埋啲好難聽嘅嘢"},{"pid":"083a86f92d74ec9f719d9d962f254c64d22ac49c","tid":245642,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"有咩缺點心知得喇，唔洗講出黎<br />\n<br />\n你父母係無腦唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0fe084db983641d643f30ff6ed44140285a1779","tid":245642,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"當住我面講架wo"},{"pid":"cc7876ffed0a85c0147a189297c34b3a8b320367","tid":245642,"uid":78325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"我老母都係咁,有次係我褲袋摷到包煙,勁大聲話你個衰仔學人食煙?!果陣成堆親戚係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cad0b5b83e9eb07fd52a2f542b7cb298adf511d","tid":245642,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我面前態度正正常常 有時行開下eg沖涼之後再返來 會偷聽到老豆老母講我壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/no